# Implementation Plan - Modern AI SaaS Frontend

Build a premium, production-level AI SaaS frontend with modern UI/UX principles (Notion/ChatGPT/Stripe inspired).

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> The application will be a **frontend-only** implementation with a mock API layer (services) to allow immediate testing and demonstration. You will need to provide your actual backend URLs in the `src/services` layer later.

> [!TIP]
> I will use **Zustand** for state management as it is more lightweight and modern for this scale of project compared to Redux, though Redux Toolkit remains an option if requested.

## Proposed Changes

### Phase 1: Foundation & Setup
- [ ] Initialize Vite + React + TypeScript project
- [ ] Setup Tailwind CSS & PostCSS
- [ ] Initialize shadcn/ui and install base components:
    - `Button`, `Input`, `Card`, `Dialog`, `DropdownMenu`, `Tabs`, `ScrollArea`, `Sheet`, `Toaster`, `Skeleton`, `Avatar`
- [ ] Setup Framer Motion for global animations
- [ ] Configure `lucide-react` for iconography

### Phase 2: Core Components & Layouts
#### [NEW] `MainLayout.tsx`
- Sidebar (collapsible) with active state management
- Top Navbar with Search (Ctrl+K), profile, and theme toggle
- Responsive container for page content

#### [NEW] `AuthLayout.tsx`
- Split-screen branding + form layout

#### [NEW] `design-system` (`globals.css`)
- Dark-mode first CSS variables
- Premium glassmorphism effects and modern typography (Inter/Geist)

### Phase 3: State Management & Services
#### [NEW] `store/`
- `useAuthStore`: Session management
- `useChatStore`: Message history and stream simulation
- `useNotesStore`: CRUD for notes
- `useUIStore`: Theme, sidebar toggle, search modal state

#### [NEW] `services/`
- `api.ts`: Base Axios instance with interceptors
- `chatService.ts`, `noteService.ts`, `fileService.ts`: Mocked API calls with simulated latency

### Phase 4: Feature Pages
#### [NEW] `ChatPage.tsx`
- Message bubbles with Tailwind styling
- Markdown support & code highlighting
- Auto-scroll and typing indicators

#### [NEW] `NotesPage.tsx`
- Split view: List navigation + Rich text inspired editor
- AI Summary integration button

#### [NEW] `FilesPage.tsx`
- Drag & Drop zone using `react-dropzone`
- Grid/List view with file previews and progress bars

### Phase 5: Advanced UI/UX
- [ ] **Command Palette**: Implementation of `cmdk` for Ctrl+K search
- [ ] **Animations**: Page transitions using `AnimatePresence`
- [ ] **Toasts**: Success/Error notifications for all actions
- [ ] **Skeletons**: Loading states for initial data fetching

